{"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)zoomLevel","symbolKind":"property","title":"zoomLevel","role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1026"}},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"double","preciseIdentifier":"c:d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"zoomLevel"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In addition to affecting the visual size and detail of features on the map,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the zoom level affects the size of the vector tiles that are loaded. At zoom","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"level 0, each tile covers the entire world map; at zoom level 1, it covers ¼","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the world; at zoom level 2, ","type":"text"},{"text":"1","type":"text"},{"text":"⁄","type":"text"},{"text":"16","type":"text"},{"text":" of the world, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"so on.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"want to animate the change, use the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-setZoomLevel:animated:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method instead.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/zoomlevel"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/zoomLevel","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The zoom level of the receiver."}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"title":"MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNMapView","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/zoomLevel":{"title":"zoomLevel","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The zoom level of the receiver.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/zoomlevel","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/zoomLevel","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}]}}}